        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=### Task\n1. Categorize the Lead Tier (A, B, or C).\n2. Generate a 2-sentence \"Personalized Hook\" for a WhatsApp/LinkedIn message.\n\n### Inputs\n- Name: {{ $json.fields.Name }}\n- Title: {{ $json.fields.Email }}\n- Company: {{ $json.fields.Company }}\n- Domain: {{ $json.fields.Domain }}\n\n### Personalization Guidelines (Wati context)\n- Focus on: How Wati's WhatsApp API can solve a specific pain point for their role (e.g., Lead response time for Sales, or automated updates for Ops).\n- Tone: Professional, helpful, and concise. No \"I hope this finds you well\" fluff.\n- Rule: Mention a specific detail to prove it's not a bot.\n\n### Output Requirement (JSON Format)\nReturn ONLY a JSON object with these two keys:\n{\n  \"lead_tier\": \"A (Enterprise) | B (Mid Market) | C (SMB)\",\n  \"personalized_hook\": \"The 2-sentence message\"\n}\n\nReturn ONLY a raw JSON object. Do NOT include Markdown formatting, backticks (```), or the word \"json\". Your response must start with { and end with }."
            }
          ]
        },
        "simplify": false,
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
          "includeMergedResponse": true
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.googleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        384,
        160
      ],
      "id": "bd1566a2-1fa5-47ab-95cc-1a23c577a373",
      "name": "Message a model",
      "credentials": {
        "googlePalmApi": {
          "id": "JSfj0qPCM80vKnv0",
          "name": "Google Gemini(PaLM) Api account"
        }
      }
